📊 Data Intelligence Dashboard
📌 Project Description

This final project is designed to build a complete data analysis and reporting solution using Excel / Google Sheets.
The project analyzes customer transaction data to generate insights, create dashboards, and visualize KPIs.

The goal is to combine formulas, analysis tools, pivot tables, and charts to create a Data Intelligence Dashboard.

